node.text: This ESP USA Viper in See-Thru Black Cherry Sunburst features stainless steel frets, Tone-Pros locking tune-o-matic bridge and tailpiece, EMG 57/66 pickups, Sperzel locking tuners, and Schaller strap locks

ESP is pleased to show you the 7th in a limited series of guitars from ESP USA. Each guitar released within the series will be completely unique and will not be limited to any one model. Every model built within the series will feature a Burl Poplar Top, Swamp Ash body, and Pau Ferro fingerboard with ESP USA at the 12th fret. This M-2 DX which is the 7th model to be released from the series will be headed to @sweetwatersound and features a Burl Poplar Top in Ruby with blue resin filler and, Swamp Ash body with single ply white binding, Pau Ferro fingerboard with single ply white binding, stainless steel frets, Floyd Rose Original locking bridge and nut, EMG 81X/85X pickups, Sperzel locking tuners, and Schaller strap locks
@thomas.youngblood with his ESP Original FRX about to go onstage with @kamelotofficial #espguitars #thomasyoungblood #kamelot
